window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>With the stunning prose and engaging characters of <i>The Silent Governess</i>, Christy Award finalist Julie Klassen whisks listeners away to Regency England for a compelling tale of romance and intrigue. Thinking she’s guilty of a crime, Olivia Keene flees her home and stumbles upon a grand estate—and a damaging secret. To ensure her silence, Lord Bradley insists she serve in his opulent manor.</p>"; 
